findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The function updateLockStatus() uses a loop to add addresses from list in _isAddressLocked array and will be aborted with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there is a long addresses list.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to modify critical settings and parameters, including dividend distribution, transaction limits, wallet addresses, and more.
